&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Compiled by:&lt;/b&gt; Dinda Anggi N. S.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;style type=&#34;text/css&#34;&gt;.din-answer-box {overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 20px;}
.din-answer-box span {
    width: 50%;
    float: left;
    padding: 10px;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;material-body&#34;&gt;
&lt;h1 class=&#39;text-center&#39;&gt;Task 1&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Complete the invitation with a phrase from the box.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;din-answer-box&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Would you like to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are going to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;div class=&#39;copy-text din-invitation&#39; style=&#34;
    line-height: 2;
    border: 2px solid #ddd;
    padding: 20px;
&#34;&gt;
Dear Zainun,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
How are you? Next Saturday on November 14th, it will be my 15th Birthday. I am having my birthday party at my house. &lt;select class=&#34;quiz-placeholder&#34; id=&#34;qAnswer1&#34;&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&amp;ndash; Choose answer &amp;ndash;&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;1&#34;&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;2&#34;&gt;Would you like to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;3&#34;&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;4&#34;&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;5&#34;&gt;We are going to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt; come? It will be a lot of fun. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There will be many people invited including our classmate. &lt;select class=&#34;quiz-placeholder&#34; id=&#34;qAnswer2&#34;&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&amp;ndash; Choose answer &amp;ndash;&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;1&#34;&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;2&#34;&gt;Would you like to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;3&#34;&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;4&#34;&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;5&#34;&gt;We are going to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt; have a Princess Party concept. Please dress up in a fairytale costume.  ^^
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I live at 7 Java Road, &lt;select class=&#34;quiz-placeholder&#34; id=&#34;qAnswer3&#34;&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&amp;ndash; Choose answer &amp;ndash;&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;1&#34;&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;2&#34;&gt;Would you like to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;3&#34;&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;4&#34;&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;5&#34;&gt;We are going to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt; You can see it is my house because I have a white fence!
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The party will be held in the evening. How about &lt;select class=&#34;quiz-placeholder&#34; id=&#34;qAnswer4&#34;&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&amp;ndash; Choose answer &amp;ndash;&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;1&#34;&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;2&#34;&gt;Would you like to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;3&#34;&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;4&#34;&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;5&#34;&gt;We are going to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;?
&lt;br&gt;It will be a very beautiful party. &lt;select class=&#34;quiz-placeholder&#34; id=&#34;qAnswer5&#34;&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&amp;ndash; Choose answer &amp;ndash;&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;1&#34;&gt;next to FISIP campus&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;2&#34;&gt;Would you like to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;3&#34;&gt;coming over at 7 P.M.&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;4&#34;&gt;Hope you can come&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;option value=&#34;5&#34;&gt;We are going to&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt; and see you at the party.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Dinda
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
